      "cookies.section6": "<h2>6. THIRD‚ÄëPARTY COOKIES ‚Äì USEFUL LINKS</h2>\n    <p>Third‚Äëparty partners have their own privacy policies:</p>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Google ‚Äì Analytics & Ads</li>\n            <li>Meta (Facebook / Instagram)</li>\n            <li>LinkedIn</li>\n            <li>Pinterest</li>\n        </ul>\n        <br>\n    <p>Learn more about targeted advertising:</p>\n        <ul>\n            <li>https://www.youronlinechoices.com/</li>\n            <li>https://optout.networkadvertising.org</li>\n        </ul>",
      "cookies.section7": "<h2>7. CHANGES TO THE COOKIE POLICY</h2>\n    <p>Da Vinci reserves the right to modify this Cookie Policy at any time.\nWe invite you to consult this page regularly.</p>",
