      "conditions.contact": "<h2>CONTACT</h2>\n    <p>For any questions related to this Statement or the exercise of your rights: <br>\n       üìß privacy@davinci-watches.com (fictional address ‚Äì training project) <br>\n       Last updated: 2025</p>",
