      "privacy.data_types": "Types of data collected: title, first name, last name, email, phone, preferences, history, IP, browser, cookies, and payment information if necessary.",
      "privacy.section2": "<h2>PURPOSES OF PROCESSING</h2>\n    <p>Your personal data is used to:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>manage your requests and orders;</li>\n        <li>provide after‚Äësales service and customer follow‚Äëup;</li>\n        <li>improve our products, services, and your user experience;</li>\n        <li>send you communications related to Da Vinci (with consent);</li>\n        <li>ensure the security and proper functioning of our site;</li>\n        <li>comply with our legal obligations.</li>\n    </ul>",
      "privacy.section3": "<h2>LEGAL BASES FOR PROCESSING</h2>\n    <p>Processing is based on: your consent, performance of a contract, our legitimate interest in improving our services, and compliance with legal obligations.</p>",
      "privacy.section4": "<h2>DATA PROTECTION</h2>\n    <p>Da Vinci implements technical and organizational measures to ensure the security, confidentiality, and integrity of your data and to prevent unauthorized access, loss, or disclosure.</p>",
      "privacy.section5": "<h2>DATA SHARING</h2>\n    <p>Your data is neither sold nor rented. It may be shared only with:\n        <ul>\n            <li>technical service providers necessary for the operation of the site or services;</li>\n            <li>partners involved in order or service management.</li>\n        </ul>\n    </p>",
      "privacy.section6": "<h2>RETENTION PERIOD</h2>\n    <p>Your personal data is retained only for the period necessary for the purposes for which it was collected, unless a legal obligation requires a longer retention period.</p>",
      "privacy.section7": "<h2>YOUR RIGHTS</h2>\n    <p>In accordance with regulations, you have the following rights: access, rectification, erasure, restriction, objection, and withdrawal of consent. To exercise your rights, contact us.</p>",
